#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid "While this would work, it would also allow the combinations \"Computer Computer\", \"Internet Computer\", \"Internet Internet\", etc. which are obviously bogus. To improve the recognition accuracy, we can try to create a grammar that better reflects what we are trying to do with simon."
